overview.en: The founding team of the Metatron project brings together outstanding elites in the financial and Internet industries. Headquartered in London, UK, it is developed by British blockchain companies, from world-renowned university scholars, and innovators who are actively involved in blockchain and digital currency related fields. The team grows and develops.
overview.zh: MTM（Metatron）项目创始团队集聚了金融、互联网、游戏行业杰出精英，总部设在英国 伦敦，由英国区块链公司开发，来自世界知名高校学者，以及积极投身于区块链 及数字货币相关领域的创新者，助力团队成长发展。目前已经研发行并落地应用有：Metatron APP 和 Singularity DAPP游戏。
